c.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443190/extras/70637ddf216ee76d36aa3e80b3216535.mp4?t=1691272128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the world at your own pace and get to know all the characters! All 200+ NPCs hace unique and fun storylines.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443190/extras/12affd76898f47525b916df0043949ee.poster.avif?t=1691272128\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443190/extras/12affd76898f47525b916df0043949ee.webm?t=1691272128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443190/extras/12affd76898f47525b916df0043949ee.mp4?t=1691272128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A charming yet disturbing game that through its themes touches on and denounces social problems that require the maturity and judgment of the player to reflect and analyze their implications responsibly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443190/extras/d5c6690ec544899789bda78d57aac5b0.poster.avif?t=1691272128\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443190/extras/d5c6690ec544899789bda78d57aac5b0.webm?t=1691272128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2443190/extras/d5c6690ec544899789bda78d57aac5b0.mp4?t=1691272128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can engage in fun side quests and minigames as well.",
